  'install.faqTitle': 'Mibvunzo Inowanzo bvunzwa',
  'install.faq1q': 'Chii chinonzi PWA?',
  'install.faq1a': 'A Progressive Web App (PWA) iwebhu app inoisa zvakananga kubva kubrowser yako kuenda kuchishandiso chako. Inoshanda senge app yemuno ine yakazara-screen modhi, push notices, uye offline rutsigiro - zvese zvisingade chitoro cheapp.',
  'install.faq2q': 'Zvakachengeteka here kuisa iyo APK?',
  'install.faq2a': 'Hongu! Yedu APK yakasainwa nedigital nechitupa cheVEX chepamutemo. Unogona kuona siginicha usati waisa. Ingoita shuwa kuti unoidhawunirodha kubva pane ino yepamutemo peji.',
  'install.faq3q': 'Iyo app inoshanda pasina Indaneti here?',
  'install.faq3a': 'Ehe, iyo app inochengeta zvakakosha zviwanikwa uchishandisa Service Worker tekinoroji. Iwe unogona kutarisa kuapp, kuona chimiro chako, uye kuwana zvakachengetwa zvemukati kunyangwe pasina internet yekubatanidza. Mitambo yekurarama inoda kubatana.',
  'install.faq4q': 'Ndinogadzirisa sei app?',
  'install.faq4a': 'Iyo PWA vhezheni inogadzirisa otomatiki pese paunoivhura. Kune APK, unozofanirwa kudhawunirodha yazvino vhezheni kubva papeji ino. Tichakuzivisa kana shanduro itsva yavepo.',
  'install.faq5q': 'Chii chinonzi AAB faira?',
  'install.faq5a': 'AAB (Android App Bundle) ndiyo yepamutemo fomati yeGoogle yekutsikisa maapuro paPlay Store. Inogadzira zvidiki, zvishandiso-zvakagadziridzwa downloads. Kuti uise parutivi, iwe unozoda Google\'s bundletool kuti ubvise maAPK mairi.',
